(59, 53, 'Asian University of Bangladesh', 'AUB', 'Professor Abulhasan M. Sadeq', 'House 25, Road 5, Sector 7 Uttara Model Town, Dhaka-1230.', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/%E0%A6%8F%E0%A6%B6%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A8+%E0%A6%87%E0%A6%89%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%AD%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%9F%E0%A6%BF+%E0%A6%85%E0%A6%AC+%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%82%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A6%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B6/@23.8696441,90.398939,21z/data=!4m12!1m6!3m5!1s0x3755c424c7a9c919:0x4d984eca7f3afda8!2z4KaP4Ka24Ka_4Kav4Ka84Ka-4KaoIOCmh-CmieCmqOCmv-CmreCmvuCmsOCnjeCmuOCmv-Cmn-CmvyDgpoXgpqwg4Kas4Ka-4KaC4Kay4Ka-4Kam4K', 'aub.png', 'asian camp.jpg', 'Dr. Muhammad Jafar Sadeq', '', 'blank-profile-picture-973460_960_720.png', 'PROFESSOR ABULHASAN M SADEQ, PH.D.', 'It gives me great pleasure to welcome you to Asian University of Bangladesh, a place of learning and scholarship, engaged in preparing young men and women to face the challenges of the new millennium.\r\n\r\nIn its efforts towards progress and development, Bangladesh needs high quality human resources, professionally sound and morally upright, equipped with the latest knowledge in multi-disciplinary fields and with technological ability. AUB commits to deliver this to the nation.\r\n\r\nEstablished in September 1996, with a few students and only two faculties housed in a small two-storied building, AUB expanded and grew quite fast. It now has five faculties, thirteen departments and a large number of students.Thus it has emerged as one of the largest private Universities in Bangladesh. This has been achieved despite our efforts to restrict expansion in the face of high demand and pressure from knowledge seekers for admission into our university. Due to AUB\'s quality education with exposure to real life situations, AUB graduates are doing very well in the job market at home as well as abroad.\r\n\r\nIf you have made up your mind to excel, to make high achievements in life and contribute to building the nation, you need the best in education and training. AUB\'s mission is to give this to you.\r\n\r\nI am sure you will find this website very useful and informative. For additional information, please refer to the AUB office, which will be glad to assist you.\r\n\r\nPlease accept my best personal wishes for your success.', 'aub vc.jpg'),
(60, 54, 'Canadian University of Bangladesh', 'CUB', 'Professor Dr. Mohammad Mahfuzul Islam', 'Plot No 99 Road No 11, C Block, Dhaka 1213', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/CUB/@23.7911576,90.4028372,21z/data=!4m12!1m6!3m5!1s0x3755c7a1f33e7d81:0xa7d45a97b942ae04!2sCUB!8m2!3d23.7911239!4d90.4029706!3m4!1s0x3755c7a1f33e7d81:0xa7d45a97b942ae04!8m2!3d23.7911239!4d90.4029706', 'cubb.png', '57bee5d0.jpg', 'Chowdhury Nafeez Sarafat', 'Dear Students\r\nCongratulations!\r\n\r\nOn behalf of the Board of Trustees and Canadian University of Bangladesh, I would like to welcome all newly admitted students at the University. Canadian University of Bangladesh was established in 2016 under Private Universities Act of 2010. The university is approved by the Ministry of Education, Government of Bangladesh and by the University Grants Commission (UGC).\r\nCanadian University of Bangladesh has made praiseworthy success within a short time and is growing rapidly in terms of academic progress by providing quality education. With our vision to become a leading university internationally in its chosen fields of education, our mission is to promote Canadian perspectives in learning, research and application, grounded in appreciation and respect for diverse cultures and Bangladeshi values. With cooperation from all concerned, I am sure, we will achieve its mission and realize its vision through quality education, training, research, entrepreneurship and community services.\r\n\r\nThe University has beautiful physical infrastructure and facilities for your learning. It has created ample opportunities for extra-curricular activities. Your participation in extra-curricular activities would help you developing your leadership quality.\r\nI wish you success in learning and future career.\r\n', 'blank-profile-picture-973460_960_720.png', 'Professor Dr. Mohammad Mahfuzul Islam ', '\r\nOur University exists for the sole purpose of transferring knowledge and experience from those of us who have it to those of us who need it. We make every effort to deliver practice based knowledge in ways that make it possible for us help each other solve our problems. This is the fundamental basis of our human existence. It is the fundamental challenge of our University. We are rewarded exclusively on the basis of how well we do this important work; how able we are to apply our cumulative knowledge and experience to solving humanities\' most intractable problems, hunger, poverty, inequality and waste.\r\n\r\n', 'zzzzzzzzzzzzzzzz vc.jpg'),
(61, 55, 'European University of Bangladesh', 'EUB', 'Prof. Dr. Mokbul Ahmed Khan', 'Rupayan Shelford, Plot # 23/6,  Block- B, Mirpur Road, Shyamoli, Dhaka- 1207.', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/%E0%A6%87%E0%A6%89%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%8B%E0%A6%AA%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A8+%E0%A6%87%E0%A6%89%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%AD%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%9F%E0%A6%BF+%E0%A6%85%E0%A6%AC+%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%82%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A6%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B6/@23.7841719,90.3451569,21z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x3755c08d0c699e55:0xc18e7cac04034b1b!8m2!3d23.784086!4d90.3452898', 'eubb.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(62, 56, 'Hamdard University Bangladesh', 'HUB', 'Professor Dr Abdul Mannan', 'Gazaria, Munshiganj', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/%E0%A6%B9%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%AE%E0%A6%A6%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%A6+%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B6%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%A6%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B2%E0%A7%9F+%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%82%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A6%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B6/@23.5980944,90.6194522,21z/data=!4m12!1m6!3m5!1s0x37544d2890d5c195:0x9c93fd428ace86e9!2z4Ka54Ka-4Kau4Kam4Kaw4KeN4KamIOCmrOCmv-CmtuCnjeCmrOCmrOCmv-CmpuCnjeCmr-CmvuCmsuCnnyDgpqzgpr7gpoLgprLgpr7gpqbgp4fgprY!8m2!3d2', 'hamdard.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(63, 57, 'Feni University', 'FU', 'Professor Dr. Md. Saifuddin Shah', '1845 Grand Trunk Road, Feni 3900', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/%E0%A6%AB%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%A8%E0%A7%80+%E0%A6%87%E0%A6%89%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%AD%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%9F%E0%A6%BF/@23.0221138,91.3849492,21z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x3753686a87477cc1:0xdea5815857bafaef!8m2!3d23.0220558!4d91.3850847', 'ffff.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(64, 58, 'Britannia University', 'BU', 'Professor Tofail Ahmed,', 'Paduar Bazar, Bishwa Road, Comilla', 'https://www.google.com/maps/place/%E0%A6%AC%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%9F%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BC%E0%A6%BE+%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B6%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%A6%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BC/@23.4199595,91.1717448,21z/data=!4m12!1m6!3m5!1s0x37547e549e703975:0xbe796f79a1f7a8a1!2z4Kas4KeN4Kaw4Ka_4Kaf4Ka-4Kao4Ka_4Kav4Ka84Ka-IOCmrOCmv-CmtuCnjeCmrOCmrOCmv-CmpuCnjeCmr-CmvuCmsuCmr-CmvA!8m2!3d23.4199448!4d91.1718628!3m4!1s0x37547e549e', 'bu.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
